id: pmc-xif2
title: Published npm package missed runtime pm SDK dependency
description: "Clean pm install npm:pm-changelog for v2026.05.24 failed to load the extension because @unbrained/pm-cli/sdk was not available inside the installed package runtime after switching to direct official SDK imports."
type: Issue
status: closed
priority: 0
tags[4]: npm,packaging,release,sdk
created_at: "2026-05-23T22:27:51.928Z"
updated_at: "2026-05-23T22:28:57.011Z"
deadline: "2026-05-24T00:00:00.000Z"
author: codex
estimated_minutes: 45
acceptance_criteria: "- package.json declares @unbrained/pm-cli as a runtime dependency for the extension.\\n- package-lock.json is updated.\\n- Local release checks pass.\\n- Corrective release v2026.05.24-1 is published.\\n- Clean pm install npm:pm-changelog exposes pm changelog generate and generates a smoke changelog."
reviewer: steve
risk: high
confidence: high
sprint: 2026-05-release
release: v2026.05.24-1
reporter: codex
severity: high
environment: "Clean temporary pm consumer installing npm:pm-changelog@2026.5.24"
repro_steps: "Run pm init, pm install npm:pm-changelog --project, then pm changelog generate in a clean temporary directory."
resolution: Added @unbrained/pm-cli as a runtime dependency so the official @unbrained/pm-cli/sdk import is available when the package is installed as a pm extension.
expected_result: The installed extension loads through the official SDK and exposes pm changelog generate.
actual_result: "package.json now declares @unbrained/pm-cli under dependencies and package-lock.json is updated. npm run release:check passed with 18 tests and zero production vulnerabilities. Clean local pm install /tmp/pm-changelog-v2026-05-24-1-local-YR2JwY loaded the extension with activation ok=1 and generated a smoke changelog with one item."
