close_reason: Runtime SDK dependency fixed and locally verified
body: "The package correctly uses the official @unbrained/pm-cli/sdk import, but package.json only had @unbrained/pm-cli in peerDependencies and devDependencies. A clean pm install npm:pm-changelog reported extension_load_failed_sdk_dependency_missing:pm-changelog and did not expose pm changelog generate."
